message.entry: Failed to find the class name specified.

usage: 
1. awtcreate(''<className>'')
 - className is a string specifying the class to be instantiated
 and invokes the no argument constructor
2. awtcreate(''<classname>'', ''<signature>'', <arg1>, ...)
 - className is same as above
 - signature is a string specifying the signature of the costructor to be invoked
 - args are the arguments corresponding to the specified signature

See help on awtcreate for more information
